➜网聊在一起10天，她被渣男泼酒精点燃，幽禁48天！6年后……
http://www.sohu.com/a/430408400_129619	34488
<p class="ql-align-center">当代友女谈恋爱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">总是吐槽自己遇到了渣男</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但什么样的男生才是真正的渣男呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小圈询问了多位好友后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">总结出了渣男的三个阶段性特征！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>1</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>初级渣男：冷暴力</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没在一起前甜言蜜语</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在一起后总嫌你黏人、嫌你不懂事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">动不动就几天不联系</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后搞得女生心态崩了闹分手</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他还会说：“那好吧。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这种撩到手就不珍惜的男人，渣男！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201108/8aaa89e848fb41e5b2c65b4271ede31b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>进阶渣男：骗钱</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每天提醒你记得吃饭、多喝热水</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">等博取你的信任后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就开始想尽各种理由管你要钱</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
